cs and 49.5% of all Literature awards.[6]"},{"pid":"5823d2af3ec0a9dc91f285a66ae467380e7a4d6e","tid":249808,"uid":57214,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-20T02:28:17.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>根本咩關係都無<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n According to 100 Years of Nobel Prize (2005), a review of Nobel prizes awarded between 1901 and 2000, 65.4% of Nobel Prize Laureates, have identified Christianity in its various forms as their religious preference (427 prizes).[5] Overall, Christians have won a total of 78.3% of all the Nobel Prizes in Peace, 72.5% in Chemistry, 65.3% in Physics, 62% in Medicine, 54% in Economics and 49.5% of all Literature awards.[6]</blockquote><br />\nNobel Prize 同IQ正相關？<br />\n你篇野根本同個Topic咩關係都無<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2770bb80a06d755f643b6c7a575fb6030db4649c","tid":249808,"uid":20170,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-20T02:54:43.000Z","msg":"自己係不可知論者 但唔講得係上面講到咁醒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c465400ae9f2efab02ad1eadbef262f3aeb7994a","tid":249808,"uid":59898,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-20T02:58:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"868403372463ef580140068aebc89df52c907278","tid":249808,"uid":20170,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-20T03:00:42.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>自己係不可知論者 但唔<span style=\"color: red;\">覺</span>得係上面講到咁醒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote>"},{"pid":"4ed061221579fab7ff05a1398cf5365a839a062d","tid":249808,"uid":79373,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-20T07:10:33.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>自己係不可知論者 但唔講得係上面講到咁醒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n+1 好多嘢係一世人未必諗到"},{"pid":"86ea80adbc47099a5a414594899dc684afa000a